subject: African Cup of Nations (Soccer)
Soccer
lead_paragraph: Bruno-Zita Mbanangoye scored from a stoppage-time free kick in host Gabon’s 3-2 win over Morocco to put the team into the African Cup of Nations quarterfinals.
